%%{init: {'theme': 'dark'}}%%
flowchart TD
    Start[LangGraph Node: Needs Deep Reasoning] --> Factory[DeepAgentFactory.create(route, context)]
    Factory --> Agent[DischargePlanningDeepAgent / ChartDeepAgent / etc.]
    
    Agent --> Planner[Planner Step<br/>What information is missing?]
    Planner --> Executor[Executor Step<br/>Call only allowed scoped tools]
    Executor --> MCPCheck{MCP Governance<br/>on tool results?}
    MCPCheck -->|Blocked| SafeFallback[Safe Fallback + Human Review Flag]
    MCPCheck -->|Allowed| Critic[Critic Step<br/>Assess confidence + blockers]
    
    Critic --> Memory[Propose Memory Candidate<br/>(non-clinical only)]
    Memory --> Governance[Memory Governance Service]
    Governance -->|Approved| Write[Write to Hindsight Memory]
    Governance -->|Blocked| AuditOnly[Audit the block only]
    
    Critic --> Output[Structured DeepAgentOutput]
    Output --> LangGraph[Return to LangGraph with citations, flags, review requirement]
    
    classDef deep fill:#1e3a8a,stroke:#3b82f6,color:#fff
    class Agent,Planner,Executor,Critic deep
